com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.grammars.javadoc

Class JavadocParserBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.puppycrawl.tools.checkstyle.grammars.javadoc.JavadocParserBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JavadocParserListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class JavadocParserBaseListener
extends Object
implements JavadocParserListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of JavadocParserListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
